==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adscript
<hw>Ad"script</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>adscriptus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>adscribere</ets> to enroll. See
<er>Ascribe</er>.]</ety> <def>Held to service as attached to the soil;
-- said of feudal serfs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adscript</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Adscript
<hw>Ad"script</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One held to
service as attached to the glebe or estate; a feudal serf.</def>
<rj><au>Bancroft.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adscriptive</ent>⟦br⟧
